# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [2.3.1] - 2019-10-22
### Added
- On student medical profile, clicking on the Admissions Immunizations Requirements header to collapse the
section collapses the Forms section instead because sections use the same element ID.  New function gives the
immunizations section a unique ID, so it can be collapsed like the others.

## [2.3.0] - 2019-09-19
### Added
- Increase sizes of grades checkboxes in Enter Grades by Class and Faculty Record Grades
### Changed
- Official Notes Unread At Top feature removed. Blackbaud's 9/18/19 update added a native Unread filter option.

## [2.2.2] - 2019-08-20
### Fixed
- Class rosters not included in previous fix for dynamically loaded students (only activity and community rosters were).

## [2.2.1] - 2019-08-20
### Fixed
- Roster student select not creating checkboxes for all students because some student cards are loaded dynamically (upon
scrolling down) for large rosters.
### Changed
- Roster student count now identifies teachers vs. students by looking for the View Relationships option in the roster
card menu.
- Roster student select now creates checkboxes for students who are group owners or activity leaders.
### Added
- Roster student select enabled for community groups.

## [2.2.0] - 2019-08-14
### Fixed
- Highlight Invalid Attendance not identifying new HRK5 block as a Homeroom block.
### Added
- Advanced List links can be copied and shared with other users.  Recipient must be running the script in order for
the link to work and run the corresponding list.

## [2.1.1] - 2019-08-12
### Fixed
- Advanced list favorites broken for list IDs with 6 or more digits.
### Added
- Advanced list IDs displayed on list of lists.

## [2.1.0] - 2019-08-08
### Added
- Highlight Row on Hover
- Manage Student Enrollment Keyboard Shortcuts
- Advanced List Role Access Keyboard Shortcuts

## [2.0.2] - 2019-08-02
### Changed
- Salutation formulas updated to reflect upcoming policy changes (and instead of &; informal salutation to use
[first] and [first] [last])

## [2.0.1] - 2019-08-01
### Fixed
- Daily Schedule Calendar was broken by Page Number Navigation enhancement.

## [2.0.0] - 2019-07-29
### Changed
- Misc changes to cleanup code and make it easier to port to other schools.

## [1.7.3] - 2019-06-04
### Changed
- Convert grad level to grade year now promotes to next grade level from June 1 instead of from August 1, to more
accurately reflect grade level promotions for summer program.

## [1.7.2] - 2019-05-08
### Added
- Admin-view-only field automatically adds when selected from the drop-down.

## [1.7.1] - 2019-04-15
### Fixed
- Salutation Formulas updated to work from parents' contact cards: auto-detects spouse in relationships.  Now correctly
generates salutations for single parents.  Fixes default Mr./Mrs. salutations that were backwards when the mother was listed
first in relationships.

## [1.7.0] - 2019-04-12
### Added
- Salutation formulas

## [1.6.11] - 2019-02-21
### Changed
- ENR-12 Shortcuts added to SUM-02 and SUM-03 forms.

## [1.6.10] - 2019-02-06
### Fixed
- (Some of) People Finder fixed to work with Blackbaud's latest update.  Core->Dashboard uses completely different code in
People Finder, so not all modifications are working on that page.

## [1.6.9] - 2019-01-17
### Fixed
- Hotfix for email links in advanced lists

## [1.6.8] - 2019-01-15
### Added
- Advanced lists containing email fields now create mailto links for each email address in the results table.

## [1.6.7] - 2019-01-14
### Added
- ENR-12 Shortcuts

## [1.6.6] - 2018-12-13
### Added
- People Finder - Click the menu button to put the cursor in the search box
- People Finder - Prevent the menu from hiding as long as the cursor is in the search box
- People Finder - If the menu is locked open, hit Escape or click on the page to hide the menu again

## [1.6.5] - 2018-11-26
### Added
- Pushpage Improvements - Increase Distribution Group List Box Size

## [1.6.4] - 2018-11-20
### Fixed
- Official notes - no longer clicks admissions only notes to mark them as read, as it breaks the page's content loader.

## [1.6.3] - 2018-11-15
### Fixed
- People Finder Quick Select updated to work with Blackbaud's latest update, which enables People Finder on mobile devices.

## [1.6.2] - 2018-11-13
### Fixed
- Email from Advanced List was failing when there was only one page of results.

## [1.6.1] - 2018-11-13
### Changed
- WYSIWYG Editor Improvements - starting height for all editor boxes can now be customized on the Settings page.

## [1.6.0] - 2018-11-13
### Added
- Official Notes Improvements - Move unread messages to top
- Official Notes Improvements - Remove notes of type Admissions Only
- Official Notes Improvements - Candidate names are now linked to their checklist page
- Email from Advanced List

## [1.5.0] - 2018-11-07
### Added
- Automatically Expand All
- [Dev] Table of contents with searchable index to easily jump to different code sections.
- [Dev] Each function run logged to console for easier debugging.
### Fixed
- Settings page not saving settings if keyboard is used to change settings.
- WYSIWYG Editor improvements not working for certain editor boxes.
### Changed
- Added info tooltips to Settings page

## [1.4.0] - 2018-11-06
### Added
- Highlight Invalid Attendance

## [1.3.0] - 2018-11-05
### Added
- WYSIWYG Editor Improvements - Default font size can be changed on Settings page
- WYSIWYG Editor Improvements - Expand button to enable increasing size of editor box

## [1.2.3] - 2018-11-01
### Added
- Current script version added to page footer
### Fixed
- Reverse attendance default no longer allows switching a locked code to Attended.

## [1.2.2] - 2018-11-01
### Fixed
- Favorite lists appearing in unintended areas

## [1.2.1] - 2018-10-31
### Changed
- Settings are now saved using browser local storage instead of cookies

## [1.2.0] - 2018-10-25
### Added
- Advanced List Favorites

## [1.1.2] - 2018-10-25
### Added
- Page number navigation for podium pages are now copied to bottom of page
### Fixed
- Student Roster Count was creating duplicate Student Count items when roster was edited on that page

## [1.1.1] - 2018-10-02
### Fixed
- Classes Menu Sort Order was broken for Elementary classes because they have no block

## [1.1.0] - 2018-09-28
### Added
- Reverse Attendance Default

## [1.0.1] - 2018-09-27
### Changed
- User Module Selector now also adds links to the "core#profile" page

## [1.0.0] - 2018-09-21
### Added
- Classes Menu Sort Order
- Classes Menu Default Page
- Settings page

## [0.10.1] - 2018-09-18
### Fixed
- Email Multiple Classes - handle cases when list of emails for class is blank

## [0.10.0] - 2018-09-14
### Added
- Email Multiple Classes from Schedule & Performance page

## [0.9.6] - 2018-09-13
### Added
- Team Roster Link to Grades

## [0.9.5] - 2018-09-12
### Changed
- Updated User Module Selector to also work on Extracurricular profile pages

## [0.9.4] - 2018-09-07
### Fixed
- Advanced list default user page menu missing for users who aren't list admins.
### Changed
- Roster Grade Level - "None" option added
